{"tid":851431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"杜特爾特宣布菲律賓共產黨為恐怖組織","createTime":"2018-10-07T06:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T13:53:31.000Z","uid":92301,"like":195,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"2d3a18eddceb6e0e0cd4543c5a2d40c4fb037e6d","tid":851431,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T06:47:56.000Z","msg":"菲律賓總統杜特蒂（Rodrigo Duterte）今簽署公告，將菲律賓共產黨（Communist Party of the Philippines）和其所屬的游擊隊「新人民軍」（New People's Army）歸為恐怖組織。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，菲律賓總統府發言人羅奎（Harry Roque）今宣布，杜特蒂以菲律賓「人類安全法」為基礎，認定菲律賓共產黨及新人民軍為恐怖組織。羅奎指出：「菲共不斷從事暴力行動，在社會散布恐慌。」<br />\n<br />\n被納入恐怖組織後，菲國的安全部門等相關單位便可以監控或凍結，國內外涉及菲共的資金流向。羅奎也表示，在菲律賓鄉村有許多商家受到菲共威脅而繳交「革命稅」，未來向菲共「繳稅」也等同於資助恐怖組織。<br />\n<br />\n菲國軍方對此表示歡迎，認為這項公告讓軍警能更為有效的執法與掃蕩。在此之前，杜特蒂並不是沒有展現與菲共和談的誠意，不過由於菲共開出的不合理條件，以及在談判的同時伏擊菲國軍警，導致談判破裂。<br />\n<br />\n不只菲律賓，美國早在2002年便已將把菲共列入恐怖組織的清單內。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2274526\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2274526&d=MCz2kgrv25DYtuinWPPTIi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=31ffb2f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2274526&h=ee611695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2274526</a>"},{"pid":"acb4e781c13ad60e01b5bda616fc9e1ba9ccc1ce","tid":851431,"uid":96465,"like":3,"dislike":31,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T06:49:51.000Z","msg":"😂🤙"},{"pid":"a45dbc08c7db5676e40519ce4c2267a364f5ff1c","tid":851431,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T06:51:22.000Z","msg":"共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfccba71771e00861b3336fd46f78701ad462d5","tid":851431,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T06:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d7e98fda817c9afeb06549ff3d19b